These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, snooker, chess, domino, scrabble, whist
House: modern, townhouse, tower, wooden, farmhouse, colonial, palace
 1. the person playing bridge is between the person playing chess and the person playing whist##2
 2. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
 3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the palace house##1
 4. the person playing domino is between the tower house and the farmhouse house##2
 5. the townhouse house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the modern house is between the wooden house and the tower house##2
 8. the townhouse house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing domino is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Game   | chess | bridge | whist | monopoly    | snooker | domino   | scrabble    |
| House         | colonial  | townhouse   | wooden | modern | tower   | palace | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: domino, backgammon, mah-jongg, go, chess, billiard, bridge
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, folk, blues, ambient, techno, salsa, trance
1. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing billiard and the fan salsa##2
3. the fan folk is on the right of the fan electronic##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the fan blues##1
5. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
6. the fan techno is on the left of the fan electronic##1
7. the fan trance is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing chess is on the left of the fan ambient##1
9. the person playing go is on the right of the fan electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Game          | chess | mah-jongg | billiard | backgammon | bridge | domino      | go  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | trance     | blues     | techno  | electronic | folk |

