.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  board-gameserman, architect, bartender, electrician, manager, mechanic, doctor
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, reading, magic-tricks, hiking, video-games, baking, dancing
 1. the manager is on the left of the board-gameserman##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the doctor##1
 4. the bartender is on the left of the mechanic##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the electrician is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the board-gameserman is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the electrician##2
 9. the board-gameserman is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the architect is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Job   | doctor | manager | board-gameserman | architect   | electrician | bartender | mechanic |
| Hobby           | video-games | baking     | reading     | magic-tricks | hiking   | board-games   | dancing    |

