.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different games are played: canasta, billiard, bridge, snooker, go, mah-jongg, poker
There are 7 different favourite colors: lavender, green, grey, mauve, ivory, aquamarine, azure
 1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is between the person playing bridge and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 7. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person playing billiard is the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes lavender is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Game      | bridge    | go  | snooker  | canasta  | poker      | mah-jongg       | billiard |
| Color   | ivory | mauve | aquamarine | azure | lavender | grey | green  |

