.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
7 different games are played: chess, go, snooker, scrabble, whist, backgammon, billiard
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, colombian, australian, egyptian, dutch, nigerian, chinese
1. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the dutch is the person playing go##1
3. the indian is between the person playing billiard and the person playing chess##2
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the dutch##1
5. the indian is in the middle##1
6. the nigerian is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the australian is on the left of the dutch##1
8. the colombian is the person playing scrabble##1
9. the person playing whist is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Game   | scrabble      | whist | chess | snooker | billiard      | go      | backgammon |
| Nationality     | colombian | nigerian | chinese       | indian | australian | dutch | egyptian |

