7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, baccarat, siglo, bongani, montecristo, alhambra
 1. the montecristo-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is between the bongani-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the baccarat-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the person watching western movies##2
10. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | martial-arts    | animation | comedy   | epic | family    | western |
| Cigar      | siglo | bluemaster | alhambra    | pall-mall | bongani    | baccarat | montecristo  |

